      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S MAGIC (1) prominent throughout and boxed on soundly to finish in the minors when second (28.01) at Bendigo in Grade 4/5. Missed the placings only try here. Has never missed the frame from eight starts from this draw, including six wins. Can find winning form. VOLTAGE STRIKE (2) was a winner (30.87) at this track two back but out of the placings last time when 6th at Geelong. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. In the mix. HURRICANE BERT (8) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when second (25.55) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool. Form here is sound including three wins. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from four starts. Hard to beat again. LEKTRA OTIS (6) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
